      <title-group>
        <article-title>Omega-3 and alpha-tocopherol provide more protection against contaminants in novel feeds for Atlantic salmon (<italic>Salmo salar</italic> L.) than omega-6 and gamma tocopherol</article-title>
      </title-group>
