                <td rowspan="1" colspan="1">&#x2003;&#x2003;&#x2003;&#x2003;&#x394;&#x394;&#x394;</td>
                <td rowspan="1" colspan="1">Deletion of <italic>BT0647&#x2013;BT0653</italic>, <italic>BT2390</italic>, and <italic>BT2396</italic></td>
              </tr>
